data.description: This wonderful Cal City, move-in ready family home offers the perfect escape from bustling city life.  The home features a modern interior design including vaulted ceilings that create an open and airy atmosphere, all on a quiet residential street. With three spacious bedrooms, including a generous master bedroom, 2 modern bathrooms, a living room with fireplace, a large dining area, and an enclosed sunroom, this home offers modern amenities at an affordable price.  This family home has over 1500 square feet of living space and a large front and back yard.  The spacious backyard comes complete with two storage sheds for all your storage needs separate from the large attached garage. This attractively priced, quality family home is the perfect opportunity to own, so set up a showing today.
